ing: 1 (15.25 ounce) can whole kernel corn, drained
1 (4.5 ounce) can chopped green chiles, undrained
1 package McCormickÂ® White Chicken Chili Seasoning Mix
des: "Cheese fanatics rejoice! This baked game day dip involves minimal prep work for maximum melty goodness. Combine crumbled feta and sharp Cheddar cheese with mayo, sour cream, canned corn, and McCormickÂ® White Chicken Chili Seasoning Mix. Bake for 20 minutes and serve with--what else? Corn chips!"
ins:
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F.
Mix all ingredients, except cilantro, in a large bowl until well blended. Spoon into a lightly greased 1 1/2- to 2-quart baking dish.
Bake 20 minutes or until heated through. Sprinkle with cilantro. Serve with corn chips or tortilla chips.
